    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep luster and no chips, scratches, or dings of any kind. Inside, the leather upholstery is pristine, still retaining its original scent and firm support, while every electronic feature and gauge functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history and a smooth, powerful engine that has been pampered throughout its life. This is a collector-grade example that requires nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
